The 2014-2020 National Competitiveness Strategy prepared by the Ministry of the Economy, Energy and the Business Environment sets forth five strategic priorities:
* improving the regulatory environment;
* partnership actions between the public and private environment;
* support factors and services;
* promoting the 10 future potential sectors;
* preparing the 2050 Generation and societal challenges.

